---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Zero Fluff" description="Learn about Zero Fluff and Andy Doyle's approach to AI implementation for small businesses.">
  <!-- Hero Section (no reveal - visible immediately) -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h1>About Zero Fluff</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted">
        30+ years of digital product experience, distilled into AI that actually delivers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach Section -->
  <section class="section reveal" style="background-color: var(--color-border);">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>The Approach</h2>
      <p>
        Every AI consultancy talks about transformation. We talk about what's actually going to happen
        on Monday morning. What process gets faster, what manual step disappears, what report writes itself.
      </p>
      <p>
        Zero Fluff exists because most businesses don't need a grand AI strategy.
        They need someone who understands their problem and builds a solution that works.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience Section -->
  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Why It Works</h2>
      <p>
        Andy Doyle has spent three decades building digital products -- from startups to enterprise,
        from first lines of code to scaling teams. He's seen every technology hype cycle come and go.
      </p>
      <p>
        The pattern is always the same: the tools that stick are the ones that solve real problems simply.
        AI is no different. The best implementations are the boring ones -- they just work,
        quietly saving time and money every day.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
      <p class="text-lg">
        If you've got a process that needs fixing or an idea that needs building,
        get in touch for a straight conversation about what AI can do for you.
      </p>
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
